About SecureAuth IdP
SecureAuth is the leader in Adaptive Authentication and information security solutions, delivering innovative secure access control for cloud, mobile, web, and VPN systems to over five million users worldwide. With Multi-factor Authentication and Single Sign-On in one solution, SecureAuth™ IdP’s unique architecture enables organizations to leverage legacy infrastructures while also embracing next generation technologies.

